Package dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.output.aicc

Class AiccMetadata

java.lang.Object
dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.output.ModuleMetadata
dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.output.aicc.AiccMetadata
public class AiccMetadata extends ModuleMetadata
Represents metadata for an AICC eLearning module, including AICC-specific fields such as course structure, assignable units, prerequisites, objectives, credit type, time limit actions, and objective relationships.

This class extends the base ModuleMetadata class to provide metadata specific to AICC modules, enabling structured storage of AICC format details.
